org.apache.taverna.provenance.item

Class WorkflowDataProvenanceItem

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.apache.taverna.provenance.item.AbstractProvenanceItem
      • org.apache.taverna.provenance.item.WorkflowDataProvenanceItem
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    ProvenanceItem

    public class WorkflowDataProvenanceItem
extends AbstractProvenanceItem
    When the WorkflowInstanceFacade for a processor receives a data token one of these is created. This is especially important for data which flows straight through a facade without going into the dispatch stack (a rare event but it can happen)
    Author:
    Ian Dunlop
